A number of weeks ago a commitment was made to provide additional
documentation for TestUtil - the open source Verification Facilitator for
unit testing all matching accessor methods on mutable objects with a single
line of test code.  In deference to the approach established by Kent Beck,
"TestUtil: By Example" chronicles a "Multi-Week Verification Sequence" of a
Fortune 5 (company) application.

 

Please see:

 

http://gtcgroup.com/util/TestUtil.By.Example.html

 

 

Feedback is welcomed,

Marvin
